                     <interp inst="t18050529-20-off115" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050529-20-off115" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18050529-20-cd116" type="crimeDate">14th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050529-20-off115 t18050529-20-cd116"></join>, a silver watch, value 20 s. a gold seal, value 10 s. and a tin box, value 2 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18050529-20-victim190" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Williams
                  <interp inst="t18050529-20-victim190" type="surname" value="Williams"></interp>
